---
canonical:
  title: Quiet Night Thoughts
  author: Li Bai
  text: |
    Bright moonlight before my bed;
    I suppose it is frost on the ground.
    I raise my head to view the bright moon,
    then lower it, thinking of my home village.
original:
  title: 靜夜思
  author: 李白
  text: |
    床前明月光
    疑是地上霜
    舉頭望明月
    低頭思故鄉
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
